がついてて", "大変だったよねぇ"]}, {"box": [388, 811, 421, 900], "vertical": true, "font_size": 33, "lines_coords": [[[388.0, 811.0], [421.0, 811.0], [421.0, 900.0], [388.0, 900.0]]], "lines": ["だなー"]}, {"box": [135, 534, 206, 659], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[176.0, 534.0], [202.0, 534.0], [202.0, 656.0], [176.0, 656.0]], [[135.0, 534.0], [161.0, 534.0], [161.0, 656.0], [135.0, 656.0]]], "lines": ["あははは", "そうそう"]}, {"box": [213, 796, 268, 1055], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25, "lines_coords": [[[241.0, 796.0], [266.0, 796.0], [266.0, 961.0], [241.0, 961.0]], [[213.0, 798.0], [238.0, 798.0], [238.0, 1055.0], [213.0, 1055.0]]], "lines": ["冬休みガッツリ", "働いたバイト代も出るし、"]}, {"box": [1156, 1121, 1217, 1391], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[1190.0, 1121.0], [1216.0, 1121.0], [1216.0, 1331.0], [1190.0, 1331.0]], [[1156.0, 1123.0], [1183.0, 1123.0], [1183.0, 1391.0], [1156.0, 1391.0]]], "lines": ["なでしこちゃんは", "バイト代いつ出るん？"]}, {"box": [721, 1145, 797, 1421], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32, "lines_coords": [[[763.0, 1145.0], [795.0, 1145.0], [795.0, 1419.0], [763.0, 1419.0]], [[721.0, 1145.0], [753.0, 1145.0], [753.0, 1421.0], [721.0, 1421.0]]], "lines": ["来週振り込まれる", "予定なんだよぅ！！"]}, {"box": [129, 1318, 211, 1545], "vertical": true, "font_size": 66, "lines_coords": [[[129.0, 1323.0], [195.0, 1318.0], [211.0, 1539.0], [146.0, 1545.0]]], "lines": ["むふふぅ"]}], "img_path": "00013.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1350, "img_height": 1920, "blocks": [{"box": [1128, 146, 1198, 470], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29, "lines_coords": [[[1164.0, 146.0], [1196.0, 146.0], [1196.0, 470.0], [1164.0, 470.0]], [[1130.0, 148.0], [1156.0, 148.0], [1156.0, 429.0], [1130.0, 429.0]]], "lines": ["おっじゃあついにあの", "ランタン買うのか？"]}, {"box": [607, 154, 639, 370], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[609.0, 155.0], [635.0, 155.0], [635.0, 369.0], [609.0, 369.0]]], "lines": ["待ち遠しくって"]}, {"box": [1151, 844, 1214, 1039], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26